OL,3,CWhy are water bills going up so much?
OL,5,FHousehold water bills in England and
OL,6,FWales are to rise by an average of
OL,7,F#123 from April 1, equating to an
OL,8,Fincrease of around #10 a month.
OL,10,FThe rise, confirmed by industry body
OL,11,FWater UK, will take the average water
OL,12,Fand wastewater bill from #480 to #603
OL,13,Ffor the next year alone.
OL,15,FHere the PA news agency breaks down
OL,16,Fwhat happens next, and what it will
OL,17,Fmean for consumers.
