OL,3,CWhy are water bills going up so much?
OL,5,FEvery five years, England and Wales'
OL,6,Fregional water suppliers submit plans
OL,7,Fto regulator Ofwat for the upcoming
OL,8,Fhalf decade.
OL,10,FThe plans include how far they can
OL,11,Fincrease bills over the period, plus
OL,12,Fhow much they will spend on upgrading
OL,13,Fdrains, sewers and reservoirs.
OL,15,FOfwat then gives a draft ruling in
OL,16,FJuly, kicking off about six months of
OL,17,Ffinal negotiations over how much firms
OL,18,Fcan charge.
