OL,3,CWhy are water bills going up so much?
OL,5,FOfwat published its final decision on
OL,6,Fbills increases in December, and Water
OL,7,FUK has just announced increases by
OL,8,Fcompany, including inflation, that
OL,9,Fwill take effect from April 1.
OL,11,F` What's the damage?
OL,13,FThe average water and wastewater bill
OL,14,Fwill increase from #480 to #603 for
OL,15,Fthe next year alone ` an increase of
OL,16,Faround #10 a month, from #40 to #50.
