OL,3,CWhy are water bills going up so much?
OL,5,FHowever millions of households face
OL,6,Feven steeper rises, with Southern
OL,7,FWater customers to see a 47% increase,
OL,8,FHafren Dyfrdwy and South West Water
OL,9,Fcustomers a 32% increase, Thames Water
OL,10,Fcustomers a 31% hike and Yorkshire
OL,11,FWater bills going up by 29%.
OL,13,FBournemouth Water customers will see a
OL,14,F32% increase to their bills.
OL,16,FThe increase will see the average
OL,17,Fyearly Southern Water bill reach #703.
OL,19,F` Why do they want to raise bills so
OL,20,Fmuch?
