OL,3,CWhy are water bills going up so much?
OL,5,FWater firms face huge problems with
OL,6,Ftheir drains, reservoirs and sewers,
OL,7,Fleading to vast amounts of pollution
OL,8,Fspilling into rivers and waterways.
OL,10,FThat means firms need to spend
OL,11,Fbillions on upgrading their systems.
OL,13,FBecause they are privatised, they also
OL,14,Fwant to turn a profit so they can keep
OL,15,Fgetting more investment from
OL,16,Fshareholders.
OL,18,FTo make matters worse, many face huge
OL,19,Fdebt piles. The 10 biggest water
OL,20,Fcompanies have about #60 billion of
OL,21,Fcombined debt.
