OL,3,CWhy are water bills going up so much?
OL,5,FRegulator Ofwat has "failed" and "run
OL,6,Fup the white flag" by announcing rises
OL,7,Fin household water bills, the chairman
OL,8,Fof an environmental campaign group
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FCharles Watson, from River Action,
OL,12,Fsaid: "The shareholders in these
OL,13,Fcompanies are just laughing all the
OL,14,Fway to the bank."
OL,16,F` Isn't Ofwat meant to stop such sharp
OL,17,Fincreases?
OL,19,FYes. Ofwat said in December that it
OL,20,Fhad "robustly" examined firms'
OL,21,Frequests to raise bills.
