OL,3,CWhy are water bills going up so much?
OL,5,FBut it actually gave firms higher bill
OL,6,Fincreases than they asked for in their
OL,7,Foriginal business plans submitted in
OL,8,Fearly 2024.
OL,10,FFor example, Anglian Water had
OL,11,Finitially asked for average annual
OL,12,Fbills to rise to #573 by 2030, a 17%
OL,13,Fincrease. Ofwat reduced that to #557
OL,14,Fin a draft ruling in July.
OL,16,FWater firms then had a chance to put
OL,17,Fforward updated requests for bill
OL,18,Fincreases. Anglian hiked its request
OL,19,Fto #649 in annual bills.
