OL,3,CWhy are water bills going up so much?
OL,5,FCritics say firms have chronically
OL,6,Funderinvested in their infrastructure
OL,7,Fsince they were privatised in 1989,
OL,8,Fwhile paying out huge shareholder
OL,9,Fdividends.
OL,11,FIn the 30 years since water firms
OL,12,Fmoved into private hands, not a single
OL,13,Fmajor reservoir has been built in
OL,14,FEngland and Wales.
OL,16,FLiberal Democrat environment spokesman
OL,17,FTim Farron said the industry was "a
OL,18,Fnational scandal".
